page.title: 20BIRDS/ANIMALS of BLINDCRAKE
page.content:
The following have been recorded:
Barn Owl, Blackbird, Bluetit, Bull- finch, Buzzard (2 pairs), Chaffinch, Crow, Curlew, Goldfinch, Great Tit, Grey Wagtail, Greenfinch, Heron, Jackdaw, Jay, Kestrel, Lapwing, Long Tailed Tit, Magpie, Mallard, Mistle Thrush, Oyster Catcher, Partridge, Pheasant, Pied Wagtail, Raven, Ring Dove, Skylark, Song Thrush, Sparrow Hawk, Starling Stonechat, Treecreeper Twite, Wood pigeon SUMMER: Cuckoo, Martin, Nightjar, Pied Flycatcher, Spotted Flycatcher, Swallow, Willow Warbler WINTER: Fieldfare
CREATURES: Deer, Field Mice, Fox, Frogs, Hedgehogs, Mink, Red Squirrel, Slow Worm, Stoat, Toads
